quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  2,142,SEJEKULU ES-SUFEHA’U MINE EN-NASI MA WE LLAHUM ‘AN KIBLETIHIMU ELLETI KANU ‘ALEJHA KUL LILLAHIL-MESHRIKU WEL-MEGRIBU JEHDI MEN JESHA’U ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  2,143,WE KEDHELIKE XHE’ALNAKUM ‘UMMETEN WESETÆN LITEKUNU SHUHEDA’E ‘ALA EN-NASI WE JEKUNE ER-RESULU ‘ALEJKUM SHEHIDÆN WE MA XHE’ALNAL-KIBLETEL-LETI KUNTE ‘ALEJHA ‘ILLA LINA’LEME MEN JETTEBI’U ER-RESULE MIMMEN JENKALIBU ‘ALA ‘AKIBEJHI WE ‘IN KANET LEKEBIRETEN ‘I
  2,144,KAD NERA TEKALLUBE WEXHHIKE FI ES-SEMA’I FELENUWELLIJENNEKE KIBLETEN TERDAHA FEWELLI WEXHHEKE SHETREL-MESXHIDIL-HERAMI WE HEJTHU MA KUNTUM FEWELLU WUXHUHEKUM SHETREHU WE ‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE LEJA’LEMUNE ‘ENNEHUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIHIM WE MALLAHU BIGAFI
  2,145,WE LE’IN ‘ETEJTEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE BIKULLI ‘AJETIN MA TEBI’U KIBLETEKE WE MA ‘ENTE BITABI’IN KIBLETEHUM WE MA BA’DUHUM BITABI’IN KIBLETE BA’DIN WE LE’INI ETTEBA’TE ‘EHWA’EHUM MIN BA’DI MA XHA’EKE MINEL-’ILMI ‘INNEKE ‘IDHÆN LEMINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  2,146,EL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE JA’RIFUNEHU KEMA JA’RIFUNE ‘EBNA’EHUM WE ‘INNE FERIKÆN MINHUM LEJEKTUMUNEL-HEKKA WE HUM JA’LEMUNE
  2,147,EL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE FELA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUMTERINE
  2,148,WE LIKULLIN WIXHHETUN HUWE MUWELLIHA FASTEBIKUL-HAJRATI ‘EJNE MA TEKUNU JE’TI BIKUMU ELLAHU XHEMI’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  2,149,WE MIN HEJTHU HAREXHTE FEWELLI WEXHHEKE SHETREL-MESXHIDIL-HERAMI WE ‘INNEHU LELHEKKU MIN RABBIKE WE MALLAHU BIGAFILIN ‘AMMA TA’MELUNE
  2,150,WE MIN HEJTHU HAREXHTE FEWELLI WEXHHEKE SHETREL-MESXHIDIL-HERAMI WE HEJTHU MA KUNTUM FEWELLU WUXHUHEKUM SHETREHU LI’ELLA JEKUNE LILNNASI ‘ALEJKUM HUXHXHETUN ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MINHUM FELA TEHSHEWHUM WE EHSHEWNI WE LI’ETIMME NI’METI ‘ALEJKUM WE LE’ALLE
  2,151,KEMA ‘ERSELNA FIKUM RESULÆN MINKUM JETLU ‘ALEJKUM ‘AJATINA WE JUZEKKIKUM WE JU’ALLIMUKUMUL-KITABE WEL-HIKMETE WE JU’ALLIMUKUM MA LEM TEKUNU TA’LEMUNE
  2,152,FADHKURUNI ‘EDHKURKUM WE ESHKURU LI WE LA TEKFURUNI
  2,153,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ESTA’INU BIS-SEBRI WE ES-SELÆTI ‘INNALL-LLAHE ME’A ES-SABIRINE
  2,154,WE LA TEKULU LIMEN JUKTELU FI SEBILI ELLAHI ‘EMWATUN BEL ‘EHJA’UN WE LEKIN LA TESH’URUNE
  2,155,WE LENEBLUWENNEKUM BISHEJ’IN MINEL-HAWFI WEL-XHU’I WE NEKSIN MINEL-’EMWLI WEL-’ENFUSI WE ETH-THEMERATI WE BESHSHIRI ES-SABIRINE
  2,156,EL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA ‘ESABET/HUM MUSIBETUN KALU ‘INNA LILLAHI WE ‘INNA ‘ILEJHI RAXHI’UNE
  2,157,‘ULA’IKE ‘ALEJHIM SELEWATUN MIN RABBIHIM WE REHMETUN WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUHTEDUNE